[{"id":"FT546233","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"If the potential energy function is given by <em>U</em>(<em>r</em>) = <em>br <sup>-</sup></em><sup>3/2</sup> + <em>c</em>, where <em>b</em> and <em>c</em> are constants, which of the following is an expression for the force on the particle?","features":[{"type":"sharedpassage","html":"<p>The following graph represents a hypothetical potential energy curve for a particle of mass <em>m.</em></p>\n\n<p><img alt=\"The figure shows a graph with U of r on the vertical axis and r on the horizontal axis. The vertical axis has tick marks above the origin at U sub 0 and 3 times U sub 0, and the horizontal axis has tick marks to the right of the origin at r sub 0 and 2 times r sub 0. A curve is plotted starting in the upper left that is decreasing to the right and concave up. A dashed horizontal reference line at U sub 0 and a dashed vertical reference line at 2 times r sub 0 meet on the curve. A dashed horizontal reference line at 3 times U sub 0 and a dashed vertical reference line at r sub 0 meet on the curve at a point above and to the left of the other point. \" height=\"185\" src=\"https://assets.learnosity.com/organisations/537/media.academicmerit.com/9514cfb0f74c99a58602a8f2f1b80afd/original.png\" width=\"300\" /></p>\n"}],"choicesHtml":["<span aria-label=\"3 b over 2 r raised to the negative 5 over 2 power\"><math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <mn>3</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <msup> <mi>r</mi> <mrow> <mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow> </msup> </mrow> </math></span>","<span aria-label=\"3 b over 2 r raised to the negative 1 over 2 power\"><math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <mn>3</mn> <mi>b</mi> </mrow> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <msup> <mi>r</mi> <mrow> <mo>−</mo> <mn>1</mn> <mo>/</mo> <mn>2</mn> </mrow> </msup> </mrow> </math></span>","<span aria-label=\"3 halves r raised to the negative 1 over 2 power\"><math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mn>3</mn> <mn>2</mn> </mfrac> <msup> <mi>r</mi> <mrow> <mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow> </msup> </mrow> </math></span>","<span aria-label=\"2 b r raised to the negative 1 over 2 power plus c r\"><math> <mrow> <mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi><msup> <mi>r</mi> <mrow> <mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow> </msup> <mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow> </math></span>","<span aria-label=\"2 b over 5 r raised to the negative 5 over 2 power plus c r\"><math> <mrow> <mfrac> <mrow> <mn>2</mn><mi>b</mi></mrow> <mn>5</mn> </mfrac> <msup> <mi>r</mi> <mrow> <mo>−</mo><mn>5</mn><mo>/</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow> </msup> <mo>+</mo><mi>c</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow> </math></span>"],"answer":-1}]